## ğŸ§© Naming Conventions

- **Directories**: Use kebab-case (e.g., `user-profile`, `auth-service`).
- **Files**: Use kebab-case with descriptive names (e.g., `login-form.tsx`, `use-auth.ts`).
- **Components**: Use PascalCase (e.g., `UserProfile`, `AuthForm`).
- **Variables and Functions**: Use camelCase with descriptive names (e.g., `handleLogin`, `fetchUserData`).

